OL,7,FAlmost half of consumers say they have
OL,8,Fsuffered poor customer service over
OL,9,Fthe last year, with many wanting more
OL,10,F"human" support from brands, a survey
OL,11,Fhas found.
OL,13,FOne in six consumers (15%) believe
OL,14,Fcustomer service standards have
OL,15,Fdeclined in the past year, according
OL,16,Fto the study for reviews site
OL,17,FTrustpilot.
