OL,7,FPoor product quality and call centre
OL,8,Fexperiences are the UK's biggest
OL,9,Fcustomer service bugbears that would
OL,10,Flead them to write a negative review,
OL,11,Fthe poll found.
OL,13,FThe study also found that consumers
OL,14,Fare turning away from AI and
OL,15,Fautomation, and instead value timely
OL,16,Fresponses to queries (54%), being able
OL,17,Fto speak to a human rather than a
OL,18,Fchatbot (51%) and getting products or
OL,19,Fservices on time (45%).
