OL,7,FMore than six in 10 (61%) say that
OL,8,Fbeing able to speak to a human rather
OL,9,Fthan a chatbot is something they would
OL,10,Flike to see more of this year, while a
OL,11,Fquarter (26%) would like to receive a
OL,12,Fmore personalised service.
OL,14,FOn average, it took 2.3 poor
OL,15,Fexperiences for a customer to share
OL,16,Ftheir frustrations with a firm.
