OL,7,FKate Delaney, vice president of
OL,8,Fmarketing at Trustpilot, said:
OL,9,F"Customers are a critical part to any
OL,10,Fbusiness, whatever the sector ` if you
OL,11,Fdon't have a happy customer, you can't
OL,12,Fgrow a successful business. That's why
OL,13,Fcustomer service is so key, and
OL,14,Fcustomers are ready to share their
OL,15,Funique experiences via reviews, both
OL,16,Fpositive and negative.
OL,18,F"Our research reveals that UK service
OL,19,Fstandards are inconsistent, with
OL,20,Fdifferences in the quality of service
OL,21,Fbeing offered across the UK.
